name: "Yellow Submarine" | Fine Art Photo Print on Canvas
description:
16x24 Fine Art Photo printed directly onto stretched Canvas over a gallery wood frame. Light weight frame is ready to hang. Image us wrapped so it extends around all sides for a clean look. 

Above print can be printed on additional mediums and custom sizes upon request. This includes prints on brushed aluminum panels, wood block or mounted on a styrene or foam core drymount and ready to frame. Email me for more info, pricing, etc. 

Many prints can be chosen from my photography portfolio as well at: ImageryByJordan.com. Email me with a description or title of the photo you'd like. 

These prints are perfect for interior design projects or livening up your home or businesses walls!
